{"article_id":"mbPN2W3ukPQbWPdK","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Friday said","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"businesses and individuals will receive a `` massive tax cut '' under a tax reform package","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"he plans to unveil next week .","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"In an interview with The Associated Press , Trump said","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"the plan will result in tax cuts for both individuals and businesses .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"He would not provide details of the plan ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"saying only","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that the tax cuts will be `` bigger","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"I believe","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"than any tax cut ever . ''","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"The president said","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"the package will be released on `` Wednesday or shortly thereafter ''","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"- just before his 100 day mark in office .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"He will face opposition in Congress","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"as the possibility of a government shutdown by the end of the month lingers .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin initially set a goal","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"of getting tax reform passed by August ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"but that deadline has slipped .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Mnuchin now says","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"the administration still hoped to get a bill passed well before the end of the year .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Mnuchin on Thursday said","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"economic growth from proposed tax cuts would come close to $ 2 trillion over 10 years .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"Steve Forbes , in an interview on Fox Business ' `` Your World With Neil Cavuto , \" said","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Trump is doing the right thing","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"by aggressively pushing for tax cuts .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"`` I think","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"he 's recognized","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"if he does n't get this economy moving in a way","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"that people visibly feel it ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"he and the Republicans are going to be in deep trouble next year , ''","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Forbes said .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"He added","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"that Trump will have to push congressional Republicans to get the tax plan through as soon as possible ,","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"because","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"even if it 's approved in the short-term ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"it will take time","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"for Americans to truly feel its effects .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"`` When you make an investment ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"it does n't mean the building rises up the next day ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"or the factory rises up the next day ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"or the services are available the next day , ''","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Forbes said .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"`` It takes time","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"to make these things happen . ... Why are n't they realistic about how the world works ? ''","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"In March , a poll found","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"that 55 percent of participants believed","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"they pay too much in taxes ,","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"The number was down from a record 63 percent in march 2015 .","depth":4},{"id":49,"text":"Americans for Tax Reform President Grover Norquist said this week","depth":3},{"id":50,"text":"that he 's confident","depth":4},{"id":51,"text":"that tax reform will be passed","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"despite recent delays .","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"Norquist said","depth":4},{"id":54,"text":"there is agreement between the White House and Republicans in the House and Senate .","depth":4},{"id":55,"text":"That includes cutting the corporate rate from 35 to 20 percent ,","depth":4},{"id"